{"tid":1638694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀察咗一陣，示威者扑爛紅綠燈根本無令到路人危險，反而係香港司機同大陸駕駛文化接軌令人危險","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:25:06.000Z","uid":28435,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bae009b544075fb1c2048f1bd74bfe71a2313185","tid":1638694,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"睇咗一陣，因為無紅綠燈，啲司機選擇咗同人鬥快<br />\n<br />\n第一同過路人鬥快，發覺無司機會係紅綠燈前收慢，大部份都係諗住同過路人鬥快，見到有人想過仲踩油渣快啲，快過路人行出嚟/嚇到路人唔敢過<br />\n<br />\n第二同其他司機鬥快，啲十字路口既地方，因為無咗紅綠燈，個個司機都鬥快行咗先，搞到塞死哂魯班鎖咁，一架kick住一架，到最後無人可以郁到<br />\n<br />\n好似警犬咁，無咁規範，人既本性就出哂嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4f56af7c1106d35a5d41c2c0b840bb9903bc53","tid":1638694,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39c69ace5a866b9355f3c5f8251546619e2b79a","tid":1638694,"uid":135211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲人驚車<br />\n明明應該係車驚人"},{"pid":"4a641e76dbed6bbedf516ea7e83eff618ca90a82","tid":1638694,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"就算有燈<br />\n個司機衝向人羣又自轉<br />\n有燈就可以控制佢地啦咩"},{"pid":"4979c62ae3c9417ede690feca13651275fc5470b","tid":1638694,"uid":5725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"標題同內文自相矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efaaa4d1392ae276c7b098e4829e0f4e4abc80c","tid":1638694,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"啲的士狗最撚明顯<br />\n揸到好似大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6533754e90e30958f9503e3c5beea7734b80ad8f","ti